248
00:25:39,246 --> 00:25:42,707
Hell, no. No, I won't, Alex.

249
00:25:44,793 --> 00:25:47,212
Not me.

250
00:25:47,296 --> 00:25:50,298
All right, then. You go tell 'em.

251
00:26:06,315 --> 00:26:08,316
