252
00:26:25,834 --> 00:26:27,877
Lugar peligroso.

253
00:26:27,962 --> 00:26:31,422
- Bad medicine, my friends.
- You got that right.

254
00:26:31,507 --> 00:26:35,718
- You grew up in a hole worse than that.
