257
00:26:43,018 --> 00:26:45,937
Yeah. Yeah. We gotta take him.

258
00:26:46,355 --> 00:26:48,690
I'd say we do.

259
00:26:51,694 --> 00:26:54,112
Hey, uh, Billy?

260
00:26:54,196 --> 00:26:57,657
Why don't you go inside
and have a look-see?

261
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:06,249
