263
00:27:34,403 --> 00:27:37,322
- I'll take two.
- Hey, Hill, want another drink?

264
00:27:37,406 --> 00:27:41,117
Got to drain it first.
I'll have Janey here give me a hand.

265
00:27:41,118 --> 00:27:43,286
