294
00:30:29,995 --> 00:30:33,164
Don't be stupid.
You know they'll be looking for us.

295
00:30:33,248 --> 00:30:36,667
Yeah, I know.
I'll be back in one minute.

296
00:30:40,631 --> 00:30:42,882
Howdy.

297
00:30:43,425 --> 00:30:48,012
- I cannot accept those. Thank you.
