00:31:28,345 --> 00:31:30,680
You tell him that.

309
00:31:34,893 --> 00:31:37,061
Yen, I'm sorry.

310
00:31:51,034 --> 00:31:53,202
So, Dick...

311
00:31:54,329 --> 00:31:56,497
who's next?

