316
00:32:20,355 --> 00:32:26,277
Horses been grazin' wild. Pretty damn
good, don't you think, Baker?

317
00:32:34,161 --> 00:32:36,954
Not that good.

318
00:32:37,039 --> 00:32:39,707
- Buenos dias, shitheads.
