322
00:32:50,719 --> 00:32:55,097
- We're with the ring, Dick.
- We're going to bury you.

323
00:32:55,098 --> 00:32:58,392
Quiet, Bonney.
We're taking you to jail. No killing.

324
00:32:58,477 --> 00:33:00,645
