338
00:34:04,793 --> 00:34:08,504
Billy, McCloskey's with us.
He's a regulator.

339
00:34:08,588 --> 00:34:12,007
- He used to ride with Murphy!
- That was a long time ago.

340
00:34:12,092 --> 00:34:15,010
