- He's been with us. We made a pact.

341
00:34:15,095 --> 00:34:17,680
- Right, McCloskey?
- Right.

342
00:34:17,764 --> 00:34:19,974
Jesus, Billy.

343
00:34:23,979 --> 00:34:26,355
Come on.

344
00:34:38,201 --> 00:34:40,494
Ah, shit. I'm sorry, McCloskey.

345
00:34:40,579 --> 00:34:43,080
It's all right.
We're all upset about John.

346
00:34:43,165 --> 00:34:45,833
I'm sorry I didn't
sniff you out sooner, traitor!

347
00:34:45,834 --> 00:34:46,959
(Richard) Billy!

348
00:34:49,337 --> 00:34:51,505
