448
00:45:16,047 --> 00:45:22,511
I could've killed you...
but I don't want to kill you. I want to eat.

449
00:45:22,512 --> 00:45:25,180
When we've finished this meal,
you rodent,

450
00:45:25,264 --> 00:45:29,309
